  "title": "Crane Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Operate cranes safely and efficiently for lifting, moving, and positioning materials.</li><li>Conduct routine inspections and maintenance checks on equipment.</li><li>Follow safety protocols and ensure compliance with site regulations.</li><li>Collaborate with site supervisors and team members to support project needs.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience as a Crane Operator in construction or related industry.</li><li>Valid Crane Operator certification / license.</li><li>Strong knowledge of safety standards and operational procedures.</li><li>Ability to work in a team and adapt to dynamic site conditions.</li></ul>",
